Package edu.brown.cs.dpark20.autocorrect

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AutocorrectConstants
    Constants class for Autocorrect.
    AutocorrectREPL
    AutocorrectREPL class, where the majority of the autocorrect commands evaluation happens.
    SmartComparator
    SmartComparator class to implement another "better" way of comparing suggestions and ranking.
    Suggestion
    Suggestion class, used to store information for each possible suggestion.
    SuggestionComparator
    SuggestionComparator class, comparator for suggestions to given word/context.
    SuggestionGenerator
    SuggestionGenerator class, made to generate suggestions based on trie, given a formatted line.
